# Sibling Project Context

- This automation repo may live beside related apps. Treat it as the automation layer for flows that may depend on one or more sibling systems.

- When sibling apps exist, document:
  - Their directory paths relative to this repo
  - Their tech stack (frontend framework, backend framework)
  - Their local ports and inter-service URLs

- When creating or updating tests, consider whether the behavior belongs to:
  - A frontend UI
  - A backend/API
  - A cross-system workflow between multiple services

- Prefer automation and documentation that make cross-system relationships explicit whenever a scenario depends on data, state, or API behavior from sibling projects.
